data.description: Discover the luxury living in this single family home, within the peaceful ''Manned''gated community of Atlantic National. Embrace the breathtaking golf course views without the hassle of membership fees, relishing in the perks of a golf club community. This highly sought-after property boasts a desirable open floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and an electric fireplace. The 2nd garage was nicely remodeled and converted to a 4th bedroom or office with AC. This home boasts Quartz Counter tops, Real wood kitchen cabinets and bathroom vanities. Fully fenced backyard with room to entertain your quests with the Outdoor built in BBQ, fridge, and sitting areas. This lovely home is located in a cul-de-sac in a great community. Easy to see.
